never allow us to hold a taskmaster hostage for more than an hour to ruin Wraith's shot at Cursed.  We also haven't trained people out of NToV, broken rotations on more than one occasion (Creator, Emperor), and encouraged our guild to over run the camps of others for shards.  <br>
<br>
I was also pretty disappointed by some posts made by a few people in Wraith that were lies about things I've said.  There was an incident in the auction channel a while back where LC was giving some loser that had ninjaed aow pants a hard time.  Desaran started running his mouth and I basically told him to kiss off and not be so cocky since his guild hadn't even killed aow yet.  Somehow that turned into &quot;Salta says we will never kill aow&quot; which turned into &quot;Salta says we will never beat cursed&quot; which ended up as &quot;Salta says we will never beat Emperor&quot;.  Then the brilliant Droz took it upon himself to post that everyone in Wraith disliked me due to my words about how crappy their guild was.  I called bs on their claims and funnily enough they completely ignored the issue from then on out (it seems that any time I do make a valid point you'll have Gurunt and Ragnarz coming to save the day by saying I'm just a troll and not to respond to what I say... it's a good strat if you like to avoid addressing the issues I've made).  The best part is that in that whole fiasco where LC guildchat was posted in a public forum there you see Salta saying that he had every expectation that Wraith would win that night against emperor.  Kind of puts a few holes in the claims some have made about me eh?  I have made comments in ooc after Wraith wiped out about how safehouse spoilers don't always work but that's a far cry from saying a guild sucks so bad they will never beat a certain mob.<br>
<br>
In any case most of the people that brand me Waif hater are stuck on things in the past.  Wraith has grown up a bit and tends to play nicer with others now and you'll notice I haven't posted much about them in ages.  Of course the same people that accuse me of needlessly holding on to past issues against Wraith are the same ones that will sit here and call everything I post a troll attempt just because of things I've said about them in the past.  I just chalk that up to the good old &quot;it's only wrong when others do it&quot; mentality.  It seems to be quite rampant!  For instance it's cool for Desi to ban me from Wraith boards for a single comment that was identical to one he made but when I as a mod of QC censor stuff censorship is the debil!  Seems the hypocrisy of some know no end.~ <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=46578" target="top">Salta</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Coercer<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.lotuscult.com">Lotus Cult</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub54.ezboard.com/bquelliousquaterstherebirth.showUserPublicProfile?gid=tunset>Tunset</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><font color=blue>Professional Thread Derailer</font><br>Woooooooooooooooo!<br><span style=background:red>I like monkeys</span></span><br>  Posts: 74<br> <font color=#00CCFF>(10/30/02 3:26:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=624.topic&index=47>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Lotus Cult and Wraith - please check this.</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://mm.dfilm.com/mm2s/mm_route.php?id=442915">mm.dfilm.com/mm2s/mm_route.php?id=442915</a><!--EZCODE